document_data.name: Huulfor Manor
document_data.mainbody: '''Huulfor Manor''' was a business located in [[Waterdeep]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Description: The building stood three stories tall.
document_data.Location: Huulfor Manor was located in the eastern section of Waterdeep's [[Waterdeep/Trades Ward|Trades Ward]] near the [[Waterdeep/City of the Dead|City of the Dead]] where [[Quill Alley]] met [[Wall Way]].
